{"about_the_game":"Explore a world where preternatural impulses shape the contours of society and join a multi-chapter adventure in Moons of True Magic, a fully voiced JRPG with a firm focus on absorbing storytelling, intricate puzzles, and gripping combat.<br><br>                                                                                                      <strong>F E A T U R E S</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Impulses</h2>Luth and Lunn, two ancient and opposing forces that have lingered since creation, steer the direction of the world around you, from the progression of your characters to the difficulty of your encounters. Choose whether you want to preserve the state of the world, unfair as it may be, or whether you'd rather risk changing it and face the potential consequences.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536220/extras/img_gif_lunn_luth_world.gif?t=1691600223\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536220/extras/KS_IMPULSES_GIF.gif?t=1691600223\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stack Battle System</h2>While you can brave the challenges outside the safety of cities as they come, the Stack battle system allows you to postpone encounters and lets you focus on exploration. Careful though, the encounters will accumulate and present themselves in a single battle, a proper test of your strength. The pace of the adventure is up to you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536220/extras/KS_STACK_GIF.gif?t=1691600223\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Intelligence System</h2>According to their intelligence rating, the vicious creatures and enemies you encounter can learn from your choices and strategize around them, choosing who to attack, which impulse to use, and forcing you to earn your victories and demonstrate your skill.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akama